# PowerShell cmdlets

## Cmdlet syntax

Bolt PowerShell cmdlets follow a verb-noun convention.

To view a full list of available cmdlets, use the `Get-Command` cmdlet:

```shell
Get-Command -Module PuppetBolt
```

